name: Greeneating
body:
### Welcome to the Page for the Hunger Game
This was a project I previously worked on at ITMS at URI. It was developed for a website used by the nutrition department in their classes. It is a small 2D quiz-based game built in Actionscript3 using Flixel. Music and Art were done by co-workers.

To try it out...

[http://protein.mts.uri.edu/MPet/GreenProj/index.php](http://protein.mts.uri.edu/MPet/GreenProj/index.php)

[Back to Main Page](http://mvpet.github.io/)
